      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in mint condition, and prospective buyers will find it to be an exceptional, like-new option that is rarely seen on the used market. The exterior is flawless, with no scratches, dents, dings, or paint imperfections of any kind \u2014 the finish retains its original factory luster and depth. All body panels are perfectly aligned, and the glass, trim, and lights are in pristine shape throughout. The interior is equally immaculate: the seats, carpeting, headliner, and dashboard show zero signs of wear, fading, or staining, and all controls, electronics, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and running perfectly, with full service history available upon request. The tires retain excellent tread depth, and the brakes, suspension, and all mechanical systems are in top working order. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that truly feels and presents like new \u2014 ideal for a buyer who demands the very best.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we are committed to full honesty with every potential buyer. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple dents, deep scratches, and faded or chipped paint in several areas. The interior has seen better days, with worn and torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general grime throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention soon, including rough idling and some warning lights on the dashboard. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the associated risks. We encourage all interested buyers to arrange an independent inspection before purchase so you know exactly what you're getting.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we believe in complete transparency with every potential buyer. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple noticeable scratches, dents, and fading paint that reflect years of use and exposure. The interior is similarly worn, with visible damage to upholstery, trim, and surfaces throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car requires attention and likely some repairs before it can be considered fully reliable for daily driving. This listing is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle, someone mechanically inclined, or a buyer seeking basic transportation at a budget price with the understanding that additional investment will be needed. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just honest representation of a high-mileage, well-used vehicle.",
